body:

For Lana, Forever Ago

Epilogue-Epictetus once said “There is only one way to happiness and that is to cease worrying about things which are beyond the power of our will.”What I believe he means is awfully simple. The…

title: Masterlist
body:
Lie Detector Test  - Y/N is a famous actress getting interviewed by James Corden, and they play a little game.

                              - (pt. II) 

                                           - (pt. III) 

                                           extra: + after 

                                                     + late late show

Record Shop - Harry has a crush on Y/N who works at a record shop.  

No Words Left to Say - Things just weren’t working out, so a letter came through. 

Jealous of the Nights - The ideal world does not exist in Y/N’s case. 

                         ^Part two: Jealous of the Love 

                         ^Part three: Jealous of the Rain

Fool’s Gold -  They fell in love at sixteen, but the last time they saw each other was seven years ago.

Furorem - An angry boy got on a bus, and Y/N just wanted to help. 

Let’s Hurt Tonight - Harry keeps a box of memories in his closet, but those memories are from his ex. 

 bestfriend!harry (request) - Y/N is Harry’s bestfriend, but Harry is Y/N’s secret love.

                      - why don’t you love me (part two to bestfriend!harry)
